snippet.title: Rabbit Hole - Early 2018 PreAlpha Footage
snippet.description:
This is some early gameplay footage of the upcoming Indie RPG game Rabbit Hole. The trio explores a mysterious red forest.

Rabbit Hole is an upcoming story-driven - RPG filled with cosmic horrors and mental illness, then wrapped in the wackiness of Alice in Wonderland.

For more info, please visit: http://playrabbithole.com
